>Description:
the procedure vector->cblock that is used in the foreign function interface
always gives an out of range error.
>How-To-Repeat:
> (list->cblock (list 1 2 3 4 5) _short)
#<cpointer>

> (vector->cblock (vector 1 2 3 4 5) _short)
. vector-ref: index 5 out of range [0, 4] for vector: #5(1 2 3 4 5)
